{"tid":422562,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］有冇巴絲有濕疹？","createTime":"2017-10-03T07:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T14:01:28.000Z","uid":21153,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a10be8085646f7e661674f5eca87561b92ec2069","tid":422562,"uid":21153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:05:09.000Z","msg":"小弟上年開始有濕疹 原因我都唔知<br />\n未算話好嚴重 但足以令我覺得好撚煩<br />\n仲要生係塊面到 睇左醫生<br />\n醫生比左藥膏我搽 搽完只係舒緩效果<br />\n完全冇好過<br />\n<br />\n請教下各位巴絲點樣處理濕疹既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">開錯台勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"cfb89f27b6aedd23ee16158ee3314ab09db0baee","tid":422562,"uid":26721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:06:26.000Z","msg":"投胎重新做人 無得醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f84297377d78852b17afdb74429856fad45326","tid":422562,"uid":21153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:06:38.000Z","msg":"屌 真係開錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e36564dd35e9dbd5bf09ac38a6926dc15bd3ab8","tid":422562,"uid":73444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:34:35.000Z","msg":"濕熱底, 睇中醫先醫好, 所以要戒口先唔發~ <br />\n不過嗰中醫退左休lu, 無得介紹俾你~ <br />\n<br />\nBTW, Ching 你係咪成日飲咖啡架, 都會有影響架~"},{"pid":"8cae090efe7d2ef10ec2c82cf9932f1baed0ba5e","tid":422562,"uid":29887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:38:14.000Z","msg":"藥房買盒蛇仔粉可以頂住先"},{"pid":"ae2e40ea024b8e34d45804b3efa2ffcc5e14cfea","tid":422562,"uid":11108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"基本上要戒口先, 食極清無油無調味會有明顯好轉, 但要斷尾要睇醫生"},{"pid":"86b8202a643ccb2302b6dd5875c3187d032e1daa","tid":422562,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"我依家咁啱等緊睇專科醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做運動好重要 做完個人又會開心啲<br />\n平時我極少食牛海鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有時轉天氣都會發<br />\n上星期發到好犀利 個專科要排成個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0465a3ae9d311e2625f20144389597aee1171483","tid":422562,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>濕熱底, 睇中醫先醫好, 所以要戒口先唔發~ <br />\n不過嗰中醫退左休lu, 無得介紹俾你~ <br />\n<br />\nBTW, Ching 你係咪成日飲咖啡架, 都會有影響架~</blockquote><br />\n奶茶咖啡都要少飲"},{"pid":"02fbe28f37751a00d6c6de18a72dffb373c317e5","tid":422562,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:58:48.000Z","msg":"D西藥會番發<br />\n<br />\n我唔想吹奏死海鹽 因為搵唔到相熟去買<br />\n<br />\n我最近用澳洲果隻羊奶補濕<br />\n<br />\n係好咗 無咁痕 出門 番屋企 臨訓 總共三次<br />\n<br />\n我覺得都係斷唔到尾 但咁樣查 無咁痕已經萬幸喇"},{"pid":"ab6df184a2d1855a5bc55409ccff687b3724de25","tid":422562,"uid":17213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:03:26.000Z","msg":"風賴係咪濕疹嘅一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea8ffb05a64377f6575dd6334ef8bd4cc147b36","tid":422562,"uid":30316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"聽講用 iphone 對治療濕疹有幫助"},{"pid":"e835f0e53903d199196df83c379703154e64e146","tid":422562,"uid":21153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>濕熱底, 睇中醫先醫好, 所以要戒口先唔發~ <br />\n不過嗰中醫退左休lu, 無得介紹俾你~ <br />\n<br />\nBTW, Ching 你係咪成日飲咖啡架, 都會有影響架~</blockquote><br />\n考dse之前喪飲 考完都冇再飲過"},{"pid":"3d009b5cbe5b1020546ce020aa3b60bd2abf01f7","tid":422562,"uid":21153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:20:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D西藥會番發<br />\n<br />\n我唔想吹奏死海鹽 因為搵唔到相熟去買<br />\n<